               <head>Biography of Mazhar Jan-i Janan and author's autobiography</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>Biography of Mazhar Jan-i Janan followed by the author's autobiography</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008108146 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85089787" n="1" xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_4431-item1">
                     <locus from="1" to="142r">ff. 1-142r</locus>
                     <note>
                        <p>Biography of <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656376.0x000001 viaf_147338829" ref="http://lccn.loc.gov/n85230986" role="subject">Mīrzā Shams al-Dīn Ḥabīb Allāh</persName> (d. 1195/1781), known as Mīrzā Maẓhar Jān-i Jānān, the poet, mystical saint, and founder of the Shamsīyah Maẓharīyah division of the Naqshbandīyah sufi order, written by his disciple Muḥammad Naʿīm Allāh Bahrāʾichī in 1204/1789-90 
                        </p>
                        <p>Short biographical account of Ḥāfiẓ Sayyid Sirāj al-Dīn Sandīlī on flyleaf </p>
                        <p>Not dated</p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_22031">Bashārāt-i Maẓharīyah dar faz̤āʾil-i ḥaz̤arāt-i ṭarīqah-'i Mujaddidīyah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_22031">بشارات مظهريّه در فضائل حضرات طريقهٔ مجدّديّه</title>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="person_f7387">Muḥammad Naʿīm Allāh Bahrāʾichī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="per" type="supplied" key="person_f7387">محمّد نعيم الله بهرائچى</persName>
                     </author>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85089787 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85010050" n="2" xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_4431-item2">
                     <locus from="142v" to="146v">ff. 142v-146v</locus>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="person_f7387">Muḥammad Naʿīm Allāh Bahrāʾichī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="per" type="supplied" key="person_f7387">محمّد نعيم الله بهرائچى</persName>
                     </author>
                     <note>
                        <p>Untitled autobiography by the Naqshbandi hagiographer of Mazhar Jan-i Janan, Muḥammad Naʿīm Allāh Bahrāʾichī, who wrote this work at the age of 56, in 1208/1793-4 </p>
                        <p>Ff. 146-149: list of chapters and subheadings, lacking folio references</p>
                        <p>Not dated</p>
                     </note>
